extends layout
block content
  div.ptl.about#content
    div.resz.ltrt
      div.wrapper
        div.row
          div.header
            h1(class=environment) A comprehensive online Myanmar dictionary
            p Uncover knowledge through linguistic expressions that you comprehend.
          div
            p
              | #[q Ordbok] is directly translated as
              |
              a(href='/definition?q=wordbook') wordbook
              |
              | in
              |
              a(href='/definition?q=norwegian') Norwegian
              |, representing a list of words with their meanings described in their own terms.
              | Therefore, #{appName} can be referred to as the #[q.mdic Myanmar dictionary] where #[q My] stands for Myanmar and #[q Ordbok] denotes a form of dictionary.
              | Since 2010, #[strong=appName] has become one of the most widely used Myanmar online dictionaries among others.
              | Currently, #[span=dictionaries_total] continental languages and #[span=locale_total] site(UI) languages are available on the platform, making it a valuable resource for users from diverse linguistic backgrounds.

        div.row
          div.header
           h2 Visits
          div.data
            p
              | Based on the recalculated visitation data from #[q=visits.created], there were a total of #[q=visits.user] unique visitors and #[q=visits.request] total visits recorded.
              | Among these visits, #[q=visits.total] were legitimate visits made by genuine #[q=visits.by] visitors, excluding bot and API requests.

        div.row
          div.dictionaries
            ol.dictionary
              each conti in dictionaries
                li(class=conti.name.toLowerCase() class={active: conti.lang.find(e=>e.id == sol.id)})
                  h3 #{conti.name}
                  ol
                    each lang in conti.lang
                      li(class=lang.id class={active: lang.id == sol.id})
                        a(data-lag=lang.id href='/dictionary/'+lang.name.toLowerCase() title=lang.my) #{lang.name}

        div.row
          div.data.social.text-center
            //- a.icon-google(title="+MyOrdbok dictionary")
            //-   span +MyOrdbok dictionary
            //- a.icon-google-circles(title="share on Google+")
            //-   span ...share on Google+
            a.icon-facebook(href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyordbok.com" target="_blank" title="share on Facebook")
              span ...share on Facebook
            a.icon-twitter(href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmyordbok.com%26amp%3Btext%3Donline%20Myanmar%20dictionary&amp;hashtags=MyOrdbok" target="_blank"  title="share on Twitter")
              span ...share on Twitter

        div.row
          div.header
           h3 Aim and Objective
          div.data
            p
              | The primary aim and objective is to serve as an online dictionary, providing practical and meaningful definitions.
              | We are committed to continually expanding the knowledge and skills essential for the learning process, ensuring ease of use and relevance for all users across various devices.
              | Our goal is to make the app accessible on widely used devices, and the content we provide is designed to cater to both beginner and advanced learners.

        div.row
          div.header
           h2.function(title="Protocol") Scheme
          div.data
            p
              | As technology advances over time, the complexity of vocabularies and semantics is addressed proactively.
              | Our app, #[strong=appName], is committed to providing users with a readable context that stimulates their imagination, enabling a better understanding of the terms they define.
              | While we continuously strive to stay up-to-date, we also ensure that vocabularies and semantics are preemptively included to enhance user experience.

        div.row
          div.header
            h2.function(title="function") Action
          div.data
            p
              | #[q=appName] will continue its commitment to working on and developing programs that align with its objectives.
              | Our primary focus will be on languages that require adaptation to cater to regional linguistic preferences (leaning).
              | By addressing these linguistic variations, we aim to ensure better regional relevance and user engagement in our app.

        div.row
          div.header
            h2.function(title="Help") Help
          div.data
            p
              | As the definitions continue to update over time, #[em=appName] would like to invite you to participate in this process.
              | If you come across any errors or have new insights that don't align with our objectives, we encourage you to notify us through the
              |
              form-links(type="feedback" text="Google forms" title="အကြောင်းကြားပေးရန်")
              |. Your feedback is valuable in helping us improve the accuracy and quality of our content. Moreover, we welcome your input on
              |
              form-links(type="suggestion" text="vocabulary and interpretation" title="ဝေါဟာရနှင့် အနက်များ")
              |, as it aids us in enhancing the overall user experience. Your contributions are highly appreciated!

        div.row
          div.header
            h2.function(title="Donate") Contribute
          div.data
            p
              | To ensure that our app, #[strong=appName], continues to thrive and provide comprehensive definitions, we rely on the generosity of users like you.
              | Your support is crucial to keep the app alive and running, in accordance with equipment specifications.
              | We kindly invite you to contribute any amount you can, as it will directly contribute to the growth and enrichment of the platform.
              | With your generosity, we aspire to provide wisdom and knowledge to all users, creating a positive impact on everyone within your reach.
              | Together, let's empower others with the gift of wisdom and knowledge!

        div.row
          div.data.donation.text-center
            div
              h3 Help us covering server expenses and ongoing development
              p
                | I would like to support to ensure its continued growth and to enable the addition of complete information.
                | My contribution will play a crucial role in helping the app thrive and provide comprehensive content.
                | I am dedicated to enhancing the app's functionality and usefulness, and I appreciate the opportunity to contribute to its success.
              form(action="https://www.paypal.com/donate" method="post" class="paypal")
                input(type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="C9PDG3T47WJ26")
                button.icon-paypal(type="submit" name="submit" title="Donate with Paypal") Donate with Paypal
              form(action="https://github.com/sponsors/khensolomon" method="get" class="github")
                button.icon-github(type="submit" title="Github Sponsor") Github Sponsor

        div.row
          div.header
            h2.function(title="Version") #{appName}
              sup #{appVersion}
          div.data
            p
              | The first version number indicates the total number of changes that have been made, while the second number represents the extent of maintenance and modifications relative to the major change.
              | The third number reflects basic needs modifications and is primarily used as the key for the
              |
              a(href="/definition?q=cookie") cookies
              |.
              | Additionally, a new cookie will be created whenever these numbers change.

        div.row.note
          div.header
           h2.function(title="Note") Note
          div.data
            ul
              li The data of the dictionary is primarily collected daily.
              li Any financial donations received will be solely dedicated to the development and improvement of #[strong=appName].
              li
                | The grammar section, directly sourced from
                |
                a(href="https://my.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%80%99%E1%80%BC%E1%80%94%E1%80%BA%E1%80%99%E1%80%AC%E1%80%9E%E1%80%92%E1%80%B9%E1%80%92%E1%80%AB" class="mtxt") မြန်မာသဒ္ဒါ
                |
                | Volumes (1) and (2), initially included some examples and exercises, but due to limited user attention, we have decided to remove it from our online app in the near future.
                ul
                  li
                    | However, the source will be preserved and remain accessible within
                    |
                    a(href="https://github.com/khensolomon/myordbok/tree/master/docs/thuddar" class="icon-github") Github repository
                    |
                    | as a reference.

block footer
  include footer